race.description: Aboriginal Family Legal Service Qnsland Maiden Plt
race.comment: JEDIAH (4) made progress finding a place in the same contest. Made good ground, but the wide gate requires a good ride. Has his share of talent and can get into the money with average luck in the run. BATE (2) peaks and is knocking on the door. This is easier than Eagle Farm last time where he was beaten less than 2L over a mile. Draws wide but can run into the finish. STRIKE ME PINK (9) is a lightly raced improver with a 2kg claim. She can get closer. WITNESS DIS (5) is a first four player.
